article_id:1434,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Event, Summertime Saviors, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e880d49b6715b3b8e657db29ec5bfc58.png,message:<div>A new event, Summertime Saviors, will start <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1594620000"></span>.</div><div>This is a limited-time event where you must defend your gate while defeating hordes of attacking enemies.</div><div>You can get items used to unlock shared skills as rewards for this event, so be sure to participate!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e880d49b6715b3b8e657db29ec5bfc58.png"></div><div><br></div><div>The Dyrenell Empire is assaulting...the beach?</div><div>They&#39;re ousting all those innocent surfers and sunbathers just so they can have their own private vacation!</div><div><br></div><div>Mikoto! Patia! You must defend New Alberia&#39;s emerging tourism industry!</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div>3. The story for Summertime Saviors will be partially voiced instead of fully voiced in Japanese.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1594360800,update_time1593776593